  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

  sha256: 1b5fc6993d04d9376185def150c857a8466cf83f16f58ce2fb09e5b166d995a5

  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

    - pip
    - python >=3.6
  run:
    - opentelemetry-exporter-zipkin-json ==1.11.1
    - opentelemetry-exporter-zipkin-proto-http ==1.11.1
    - python >=3.6

    - opentelemetry

  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip
